CRYPTOGRAPHIC SOFTWARE NOTICE

This software implements cryptographic protocols for Bitcoin Silent Payments
(BIP-352). Users are responsible for:

1. Auditing the cryptographic implementation before production use
2. Securing private keys and sensitive data
3. Understanding the privacy implications of their usage patterns
4. Complying with applicable laws and regulations

THE AUTHORS PROVIDE NO WARRANTY REGARDING THE SECURITY OR CORRECTNESS OF THIS
IMPLEMENTATION. USE AT YOUR OWN RISK. LOSS OF FUNDS MAY OCCUR DUE TO BUGS OR
MISUSE.
